ig_artist.full_name: Mikhail Gribov | 7 fig Business and Social Media Coach

caption.text:
I built a 7-figure business with the help of a coach👇

After hitting a plateau in revenue in 2022, I realized I needed to change something.

That’s when I came up with the idea to build an agency and sell high-ticket offers

Instead of low/mid ticket offers

We ran a test, helped 20+ content creators and entrepreneurs for free build and scale their offers to 5-6 figures using Instagram, and then it was time to start selling our services.

But the problem was… I didn’t know how to sell.

I had never sold anything on sales calls… only in DMs.

So, I hired a coaching company that taught me high-ticket sales.

It took some time, good coaching and repetition 

That’s how I went from $0 to $100k/month in revenue pretty quickly.

And then scaled this offer to $600k/month in a year.

The same applies to any skill you don’t have.

If you have an offer but struggle to get clients, Instagram is the best platform to get them for free.

You just need the right strategy, patience, and the right coach.

That’s what we do!

Comment COACH, and I’ll DM you my training.

It will help you get more followers and clients on Instagram to scale your offer to 6-7 figures in sales.

caption.text:
How to Get More Views on Instagram👇

👉 Create a Great Caption for Your Reel!

1️⃣ First Sentence is the Key

Don’t start your caption like “once upon a time.”

Example: “So today I want to talk about… - BORING🥱”

Instead, you have to grab your audience’s attention the same way you do with your reel’s hooks.

Like: “You will fail if you make this mistake again👇”

Otherwise, they will scroll past your content, and you’ll get fewer views.

2️⃣ Good Caption Ideas Are:

- The secret to ____ (e.g., gaining followers)
- You will never ____ (specific desired outcome) if you ____ (mistake most people in your niche make)
- What NOT to do if you want ___ (specific desired outcome)
- You need to stop ____ (e.g., deleting your reels)
- The biggest mistake all ___ (e.g., realtors) make
- This is a reminder to ___ (e.g., stay fit)
- Here’s the shortcut to ___ (e.g., getting clients on Insta)
- How to ___ (e.g., avoid burnout)
- Why is nobody talking about ___ (e.g., self-love)
- This is going to be controversial, but ___
- How to ____ (specific desired outcome)?

3️⃣ Captions Should Be Valuable!

No more BS information.

It’s easy to write a one-line caption. For example, a call to action like “Follow for more.”

But you will get better results if you actually provide value to your audience.

Like I’m doing right now for this caption.

Thus, you will get more saves and shares for your reel, resulting in more views!

Value ideas for your caption: Step-by-step plans, client results, your transformation story, quick and easy hacks.

P.S.

If you haven’t grown on Instagram over the last 3 months, stop and get help.

You won’t grow by doing the same thing that doesn’t get you results.

My team and I can help you get more followers and clients and grow your online business on Instagram.

Comment ➕ and I’ll dm you the details

ig_artist.full_name: Mikhail Gribov | 7 fig Business and Social Media Coach

caption.text:
TOP products ideas to make 💰

If you have 1000 reels views, you can make multiple 4-5 figures a month in sales

ORGANICALLY

with zero ad spend!

And if you have more views, like me, 50k+

you can make multiple 6 figures a month!

I know these numbers might look crazy at first, but it’s just because you don’t know how to do it.

The very first step we take with our clients is to come up with the right product or service idea.

We call it “Product/Account fit”

Among your followers you have potential low ticket buyers, mid and high ticket buyers.

And for example if you sell only low ticket offer on a large account - That’s how you lose money.

Here are the best product ideas TODAY to build your multiple 5-figure/month online business with:

1️⃣ Coaching (1:1/Group) 
2️⃣ DFY Service (Done For You) 
3️⃣ Online Course
4️⃣ 1-2 Hour Consultation
5️⃣ Ebook (only if you are a beginner)

BUT!

If you come up with the wrong product idea, you may “lose” money, like I did 2 years ago

At that point, I already had a lot of followers, but I came up with a bad offer idea that didn’t fit my audience—a low-ticket ebook.

So instead of making $20,000-$30,000 a month with a mid or high-ticket offer, I barely made $5,000. It was decent money for me, but I could’ve made so much more…

The same applies to your account. If you launch the wrong offer, you will make $100 instead of $10,000!

This year Instagram revealed a new official guide on how to grow on Instagram with reels in 2024

It’s an 84-page document with different content ideas and tips.

C0mment PDF, and I’ll DM you the guide right now.

I also chose 6 most interesting tips from it and recorded my feedback. You will find them there
